description:
George Noory and Dr. Cyril Wecht, along with author Charles Bosworth, discuss Wecht's investigations into some of the most high profile deaths in America, including JonBenet Ramsey, Robert F. Kennedy, Elvis Presley, Michael Jackson and Whitney Houston.
